If I had seen it for sale for lets say 500pp I might have bought it, but not a single pp more.<br>
<br>
Why?<br>
<br>
BO3:<br>
Increase STR by 50 <br>
Increase Attack Speed by 60% <br>
Increase AC by 13 <br>
<br>
BO4:<br>
Increase STR by 60 <br>
Increase Attack Speed by 65% <br>
Increase AC by 16 <br>
<br>
com'on, 5% more haste (effectively meaning an increase of about 3% (165%/160% or 176%/171% (with Muzzle))<br>
3 more AC? wow...that will make my Pet to take much less damage I bet. <br>
10 more Strength...hmmm, no clue how helpful that is.<br>
<br>
Now lets take BO5:<br>
Increase AC by 22 <br>
Increase STR by 80 <br>
Increase Attack Speed by 85% <br>
Increase ATK by 40 <br>
<br>
Now THAT I do call an upgrade, but BO4 is a joke compared to BO3 imho.<br>
